Placeholder jQuery Plugin v0.3b
-------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2011 Shahal Tharique. Licensed under MIT License


Overview
--------

A simple jQuery plugin that overrides the input box's placeholder attribute. 


Usage
-----

// Include the jquery.js and jquery.placeholder.js in your html file.

<script type='text/javascript' src='jquery.js'></script> 
<script type='text/javascript' src='jquery.placeholder.js'></script>


// Add the required placeholder value to the placeholder attribute of the input box. 

<input type='text' name='username' placeholder='Username' class='jquery-placeholder-test' />

//Now call the .placeholder() function on the required input box's jQuery object.

$(document).ready(function(){
	$('.jquery-placeholder-test').placeholder();
})

